instruction: Verify that Ndum_sdm_get can be triggered for slave IMSI of HLR based multiple device subscriber once subscriber moving from 5GC to VoWifi.
response:
...	[Pre-Requisite]
...	[Execution Steps]
...	1. Set EME FF on, PDU FF ON, QueryUdmEmergInfoAlways off.
...	2. Set nudm-sdm-subscription profile ahead.
...	3. Send slave Imsi Swx-MAR Swx-SAR SAT=reg. Once Get is triggered then response HSS with pgwInfo.
...	[Expected Result]
...	1.FFs are configed successfully.
...	2.MAA:RC:2001.SAA:RC:2001. Nudm-SDM-Get is triggered to UDM. The hssEmergencyInfo updated in DB and included in SAA.
[Tags]	CRITICAL	FUNCTIONAL	HTTP2	ST_RG_6139	ndum_sdm_get	SEQUENTIAL	ALL_HW	WM_UAT	HSSFT_ATMN
[Setup]	Setup TC001
Run Keyword And Continue On Failure	ST_RG_6139_HSS_FT_TC001_SAR
Run Keyword And Continue On Failure	ST_RG_6139_HSS_FT_TC001_Nudm_SDM_Get
Run Keyword And Continue On Failure	ST_RG_6139_HSS_FT_TC001_SAA
Run Keyword And Continue On Failure	Wait Until Keyword Succeeds	10	2sec	ST_RG_6139_HSS_FT_TC001_Nudm_SDM_Check_DB
[Teardown]	Teardown TC001

instruction: Verify the full set of own APN data, neither useOwnDataPerSubImsi attribute or specific APN data is not allowed to be provisioned for the subordinate imsis of HLR-Based Multi SIM if AEP FF off
response:
...	Pre-Requisite
...	0. MultiIMSI FF is enabled.	AEP FF AllowApnListPerImsi is off
...	1. create 20 auc sub and modify the HLRbased multisim to have 1 master 19 slaves, Master(IMSI) is with APN1_Static, APN2_Dynamic, APN3_Dynamic
...	Execution Steps
...	1. Add the supported APN data for subordinate IMSI: Slave1(IMSI1) is without useOwnDataPerSubImsi but APN4_Static(with only PGW info)
...	2. Add the full set of APN data for subordinate IMSI: Slave2(IMSI2) is without useOwnDataPerSubImsi but APN4_Static(with PGW info and ips)
...	3. dd the new supported attribute for subordinate IMSI: Slave6(IMSI6) is with useOwnDataPerSubImsi=useOwnApnList but without own APN
...	4. Add epsSharedUserProfile for slave1
...	5. Add roamSubscription for slave1
...	Expected Result
...	1. Slave1 update succcessfully as limited APN Info can be updated for subordinate IMSIs when AEP FF off(Legacy behavior);
...	2. Slave2 udpate failed as only limited APN info(eg: PWG info) can be proviooned for subordinate IMSIs if AEP FF off;
...	3. Slave6 udpate failed as useOwnDataPerSubImsi is not allowed when AEP FF is off
...	4. spml success but there is no SUP provisioned for slave1 (lagacy behavior)
...	5. spml success but there is no roamingSubscription provisioned for slave1 (lagacy behavior)

instruction: Verify the own APN data can be Modified successfully for all the subordinate imsis of HLR-Based Multi SIM.
response:
...	Pre-Requisite
...	0. MultiIMSI FF is enabled.
...	1. Create a subscriber MSUB1 with 1 master IMSI and 19 secondary IMSI.
...	Execution Steps
...	1. Modify MSUB1 by configuration own APN data for all the subordinate IMSIs
...		Master(IMSI) is with APN1_Static, APN2_Dynamic, APN3_Dynamic
...		Slave1(IMSI1) is with useOwnApnListPerImsi=FALSE and APN4_Static
...		Slave2(IMSI2) is with useOwnApnListPerImsi=TRUE and APN2_Dynamic, APN4_Static
...		Slave3(IMSI3) is with useOwnApnListPerImsi=TRUE and APN1_Static,APN2_Dynamic,APN4 Static
...		Slave4(IMSI4) is with useOwnApnListPerImsi=TRUE and APN1_Static,APN2_Dynamic,APN4 Static
...		Slave5(IMSI5) is with useOwnApnListPerImsi=TRUE and APN4_Static
...		Slave6(IMSI6) is without own APN
...	2. Search subscriber MSUB1.
...	3. modify APN info for sobordinate imsis:
...		Slave1(IMSI1) useOwnApnListPerImsi from false to true
...		Slave2(IMSI2) APN4_Static from pgw1 to pgw2
...		Slave3(IMSI3) useOwnApnListPerImsi from true to false
...	4. modify PGW info of Dynamic APN  for sobordinate imsis(which is invalid):
...		Slave4(IMSI4) APN2_Dynamic from PGW1 tp PGW2
...	Expected Result
...	1. Sub is modifed successfully
...	2. Sub can be searched successfully and each subordinate IMSIs has it's own APN data
...	3. modifed successfully
...	4. Modify failed as dynamic APN can not be updated updated via provision
[Tags]	CRITICAL	FUNCTIONAL	AEP	CNSREQ_198	HSSFT_P0	MultiSIM	ALL_HW
[Setup]	Setup ST_RG_5426_AEP_FT_TC202

ST_RG_5426_AEP_FT_TC202_queryDB1
ST_RG_5426_AEP_FT_TC202_ModifyAPN_Invalid
